    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Echo flies around a flank to threaten the backline with Sticky Bombs and Focusing Beam, using Duplicate on a high-value target to briefly borrow their kit for a fight-winning burst.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>She has no self-sustain and dies quickly to focused hitscan fire; a whiffed Duplicate on the wrong target wastes her ultimate almost entirely.</p>"
